During the day, there will be a box reserved for all the guests and 5 exclusive rounds will be held in which I will race on competition motorcycles alongside great riders such as Marco Lucchinelli, Michele Pirro and Dario Marchetti.

The prize includes:
- Roundtrip flight for two people ✈️
